<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="surprise-n">surprise <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sə'praɪz/    美 /sər'praɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-c">1.★ <strong>[U] &amp; [C] 惊奇；诧异：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He expressed surprise that no one had offered to help. 
谁都不肯帮忙，他感到诧异。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 使人吃惊的事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We have a Christmas surprise for you. 
我们要给你一份意想不到的圣诞礼物。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-surprise">in surprise</h3>
<p>1.<strong>惊奇地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>“How did you come to know it?” asked the man in surprise. 
那人惊奇地问：“你是怎么知道的？”</p></div>

<h3 id="take-by-surprise">take ... by surprise</h3>
<p>1.<strong>使…吃惊；突袭：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The question took the professor by surprise. 
那个问题使教授大感意外。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The troop were taken by surprise while sleeping. 
部队在睡梦中遭到突袭。</p></div>

<h3 id="to-sbs-surprise-to-the-surprise-of-sb">to sb’s surprise / to the surprise of sb</h3>
<p>1.<strong>使某人吃惊的是：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To my surprise, many of them expressed disappointment.
让我惊讶的是，他们中很多人表示失望。</p><footer>2008 湖北</footer></div></div>